View.Name: DeploymentHealthSurvey
View.CheckCode:
DefineVariables DEFINE ERHMS NETOBJECT "ERHMS Info Manager.Integration" DEFINE WorkerId TEXTINPUT End-DefineVariables
Field WorkerInfo_GetGlobalRecordId Click ASSIGN WorkerId = ERHMS.GetWorkerId(WorkerInfo_FirstName, WorkerInfo_LastName, WorkerInfo_EmailAddress, WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId) IF WorkerId <> "" THEN ASSIGN WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId = WorkerId END-IF End-Click End-Field

Field.Name: Instructions
Field.PromptText: Describe the hazards you were exposed to, the personal protective equipment you wore, and the injuries/illnesses you experienced during this deployment. Consider only the time period since your previous survey. If this is your first survey, consider the entire time period since the beginning of this deployment.

Field.Name: WasExposed
Field.PromptText: Were you exposed to any hazards?

Field.Name: HazardsSkipLabel
Field.PromptText: If not, skip the rest of this section.

Field.Name: Hazards
Field.PromptText: What hazards were you exposed to? Check all that apply.

Field.Name: PPESkipLabel
Field.PromptText: If not, skip the rest of this section.

Field.Name: PPE
Field.PromptText: What PPE did you wear? Check all that apply.

Field.Name: EyeProtection
Field.PromptText: Eye protection (safety glasses, face shield, etc.)

Field.Name: InjuriesSkipLabel
Field.PromptText: If not, skip the rest of this section.

Field.Name: Injuries
Field.PromptText: What injuries/illnesses did you experience? Check all that apply.

Field.Name: InjuriesDescription
Field.PromptText: Describe the cause, nature, and severity of these injuries/illnesses.

Field.Name: Witnesses
Field.PromptText: Who else was present at the time of these injuries/illnesses?

Field.Name: ReceivedMedicalTreatment
Field.PromptText: Did you receive medical treatment for these injuries/illnesses?
